Witnessed the most beautiful and organised Mother’s Day celebration. Mom and me time at Emerald Mall, Lucknow.

Time 3-8pm 
It has the various activities like candle, making DIY nail Art Mehndi art live music clown activity which was absolutely free of cost. 

also, I had the amazing shopping experience at Emerald Mall which has the best offers and the best shopping experience. Also I love the theme of fashion walk with mother because all mothers Are our first ever role model.

A special thanks to  @daizysonalmishra for organising such a 😍 event in which me and my mom had the best time ever of our life. Looking forward for such amazing event more.
